                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9332" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1397</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1041 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智能税策：如何优化手机巨头的税负布局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Smart Tax Policy: How to Optimize the Tax Layout of Mobile Phone Giants</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵红，武雪瑶，耿磊，张慧慧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳闪回科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造企业；纳税筹划；全链条工作体系；增值税</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Manufacturing companies, tax planning, whole chain working system, VAT</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HQ企业成立于2005年，由赵总和他的两位大学同学一同创立，如今已是一家全球领先的手机原始设计制造商（ODM）。纵观现在的电子设备制造行业，行业的利润被压缩，企业进行内部的税收优化迫在眉睫。纳税筹划的专业性和政策性较强，之前没有得到足够的重视，HQ企业经营的各个环节中都未培养进行税收筹划的意识，企业的税收筹划面临着从0到1的艰难困境。本案例基于税务筹划的视角，针对HQ企业在经营过程中所遇到的增值税问题进行探究，着重剖析各税法条文中的相关优惠政策，寻找全链条工作体系下各个环节的最优纳税筹划方案。案例旨在引导学生理解和学习增值税的概念、扣除项目的归属，以及认识企业增值税的清算条件和方法，从而掌握纳税筹划的基本思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Founded in 2005 by Mr Zhao and two of his university classmates, HQ Enterprises is now a leading global original design manufacturer (ODM) of mobile phones. Throughout the electronic equipment manufacturing industry nowadays, the profit of the industry is compressed, and it is urgent for enterprises to carry out internal tax optimisation. The professionalism and policy of tax planning is strong, which has not been given enough attention before, and HQ has not cultivated the awareness of tax planning in all aspects of business operation, and the enterprise&#39;s tax planning is facing the difficult dilemma of going from 0 to 1. Based on the perspective of tax planning, this case explores the value-added tax (VAT) problems encountered by HQ Enterprise in the course of its operation, focuses on analysing the relevant preferential policies in the tax laws, and searches for the optimal tax planning solutions for each link of the whole chain working system. The case aims to guide students to understand and learn the concept of value-added tax, the attribution of deductions, as well as to recognise the conditions and methods of enterprise value-added tax clearance, so as to master the basic ideas of tax planning…</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税务筹划》、《中国税制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纳税筹划理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
